mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Datebook", "On The Record and Record Report", "Feature Fashion", "As I See It", "Vox Saltator", "Teaching Square Dancing-Part II", "Cal Golden Calls Again", "The Dancers Walk-Thru", "Lift and Use", "Homes for Square Dancing", "Interview: Les Gotcher", "Style Series: The Uncomfortables", "National Convention", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "SIO Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Joe Young", "Paging the Round Dancers: Clark and Maxine Smith", "Current Best Sellers", and "Experimental Lab".
